title: Culinary Insight
description: This is a data science project for DSC80 at UC San Diego. We decided to analyze this data as it allows us to discover new recipes to try in our own kitchen and better understand the nutritional value and benefits of different foods. This knowledge helps us make informed choices to support our fitness goals while still enjoying delicious and healthy meals.

title: Music Genre Prediction
description: This is a data science project for COGS108 at UC San Diego. We analyzed Spotify data to explore how audio features like danceability, energy, and popularity correlate with music genres. Our findings help improve music recommendations and deepen our understanding of the characteristics that define different genres..
